            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><rs key="#Transactional_breve">Breve</rs> recordationis, qualiter domna <rs
                            key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess #Transactional_breve #Commutatio #Mansi"
                            ref="#people/125">Mathildis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Commutatio">commutationem</rs> fecit cum <rs key="#Archpriests"
                            >archipresbytero</rs>
                        <persName
                            key="#Archpriests #Transactional_breve #Commutatio #Mansi #Witness"
                            >Michaele</persName>, <orgName
                            key="#Baptismal_churches #Archpriests #Transactional_breve #Commutatio #Mansi #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2096"><rs key="#Baptismal_churches">plebis</rs>
                            Sancti Martini</orgName> quae posita est iuxta locum qui dicitur
                            <placeName key="#Baptismal_churches">Casalittum</placeName>, ex quodam
                            <rs key="#Mansi">manso</rs>, qui positus est in <geogName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#estates/80"><rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Curtes #Mansi" ref="#places/362"
                            >Villulae</placeName></geogName>, qui laboratur per
                            <persName>Ioannem</persName> de <persName>Bonizo</persName>, qui mansus
                        pertinebat ad <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2097">Sancti
                            Erasmi</orgName> de <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2418"
                            >Gubernulo</placeName>, cappellam predictae plebis, pro quodam manso
                        iacente in curte praefatae plebis, qui laboratur per
                            <persName>Albertum</persName> de <persName>Venerando</persName>.
                        Refutavit etiam praedictus archipresbyter quicquid prędicto manso ad
                        ecclesiam Sancti Herasmi pertinebat in manus dominae comitissae Mathildis,
                        tali videlicet tenore, ut neque a praedictus archipresbyter, neque aliquis
                        illius successor vel alia quaelibet persona praedicto manso <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Mansi #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">Sancti
                            Benedicti iuxta Padum</orgName>, cui prędicta comitissa Mathildis eundem
                        mansum <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs> dedit,
                        in aliquo ullo tempore molestare aut inquietare praesumat. Si quis vero,
                        quod absit, sive praedictus archipresbyter seu aliqua persona praefatum
                        monasterium ex praedicto manso in aliquo molestare praesumpserit ecclesiam
                        Sancti Herasmi <rs key="#Penalty">decem libras bonorum denariorum Lucensis
                            monetae</rs> Sancti Benedicti monasterio per obligationem praedicti
                        archipresbyteri componere debet. Hac tamen praedicta commutatione in sua
                        firmitate permanente in perpetuum. lnterfuerunt <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testes</rs>: <persName key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio"
                            ref="#people/2199">Ugo</persName> de <persName ref="#people/3510"
                            >Manfredo</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio">Tebertus</persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/15">Nonantula</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio">Azo</persName> de
                            <placeName>Sala</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio">Ribaldus</persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/72">Vigniola</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio">Nordulus</persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/2922">Castello vetere</placeName>, et alii
                        quamplures. Actum est ad <placeName>Pontem Ducis</placeName>, Millesimo
                        Centesimo nono, indictione secunda, <rs key="#Writer">per manum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Other_clerics #Transactional_breve #Commutatio"
                            ref="#people/3508">Ribaldi</persName> eiusdem comitissae Mathildis <rs
                            key="#Other_clerics">cappellani</rs>, pridie nonas novembris. Ego
                            <persName key="#Judge #Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio"
                            >Ubaldus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> interfui et subscripsi. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness #Transactional_breve #Commutatio">Conon</persName>
                        interfui et subscripsi. Ego Michael archipresbyter confirmavi et subscripsi. </ab>
